UPDATE dim_partner
SET GEO_POINT = cast('POINT('||trim(longitude)||' '||trim(latitude)||')' as st_geometry)
WHERE longitude IS NOT NULL  and latitude IS NOT NULL

MERGE INTO dim_partner_group AS tgt 
USING 
	(SELECT 'SAMS_CLUB' AS partner_group_pid, 'Sams Club' AS partner_group_name, 'Sams Club' AS partner_group_description,  'SAMPLE' AS source_system, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS created_at, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS updated_at, 0 as is_deleted)  AS src
ON tgt.partner_group_pid = src.partner_group_pid AND tgt.source_system = src.source_system
WHEN MATCHED THEN
	UPDATE SET partner_group_name = src.partner_group_name, partner_group_description = src.partner_group_description, updated_at = src.updated_at,is_deleted = src.is_deleted
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
	INSERT (partner_group_pid, partner_group_name,
		partner_group_description, source_system, created_at, updated_at,
		is_deleted) VALUES (src.partner_group_pid, src.partner_group_name, src.partner_group_description, src.source_system, src.created_at, src.updated_at, src.is_deleted);

UPDATE   dim_person
FROM (
	SELECT person_key, lat, lng
	FROM dim_person
	JOIN consumer_data
		ON dim_person.consumer_data_key = consumer_data.consumer_data_key
	WHERE consumer_match_conf_lvl in (0,1)
	) cnsmr

SET geo_point = cast('POINT('||trim(lng)||' '||trim(lat)||')' as st_geometry)
WHERE dim_person.person_key = cnsmr.person_key
